{"root":{"data":{"id":"d1lxmdixesqo","created":1716965917560,"text":"mNGS-AST流程：短reads"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lxo015j0g0","created":1716966044916,"text":"数据集来源","priority":1,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lxp3sov5s0","created":1716966131475,"text":"临床分离株基因组作为训练集"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxveospreo","created":1716966625369,"text":"使用ART软件(版本2.5.8)构建模拟数据","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lxsbk1eps0","created":1716966383459,"text":"参数: -sssns50 -l 75 -f 5 -nf 0 -rs 1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxtja4p4hs","created":1716966478638,"text":"为了筛选关键的ARG亚型，模拟不同数据量的Illumina SE75序列，\n评估和总结均匀性覆盖的正常范围，确定均匀性覆盖阈值以滤除假阳性结果"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxyc5tr9q8","created":1716966854961,"text":"模拟不同梯度基因组测序深度","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lxwx38fmdc","created":1716966743789,"text":"0.01x、0.02x、0.03x、0.05x"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxwzxnvn5s","created":1716966749982,"text":"0.1X、0.2x、0.3x、0.4x、0.5x、0.6x、0.7x、0.8x、0.9x"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxx3ifqzuo","created":1716966757769,"text":"1x、2x、3x、5x、10x、30x"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxyjm2xnnk","created":1716966871182,"text":"评估测序数据量对预测模型性能的影响，确定各模型的最低测序深度"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxz7x3m1hc","created":1716966924091,"text":"在30倍测序深度下，参照基于装配的ARG检测计算灵敏度、特异性和准确性，评估基于读取的ARG检测的检测性能"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lxzdv3xuyo","created":1716966937031,"text":"开发ARG注释和分型流程","priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1ly64h7or9c","created":1716967465149,"text":"BLASTN直接将未组装的mNGS reads与ARG参考数据库进行比对，确定ARG亚型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1ly6xmwlwxs","created":1716967528620,"text":"对于每个read的注释"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lyw6r3rta8","created":1716969507569,"text":"首先使用贪婪算法和特定的对齐策略来识别\nARG的真或假阳性，并过滤掉假阳结果","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":2}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lyyb2i8u0w","created":1716969673694,"text":"序列覆盖不均匀的ARGs是假阳"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lyytu0ka2o","created":1716969714539,"text":"对于gyrA等变异的ARG，频率< 0.2的变异位点假定是假阳"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lywl8igwzk","created":1716969539096,"text":"然后使用LCA方法对检测到的剩余ARGs进行注释","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":4}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1ly778nhssg","created":1716967549526,"text":"推断注释到的ARGs的物种来源"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d1lyif5pgfsw","created":1716968428768,"text":"主要根据ARGs的计算拷贝数是否在假设的基因-物种隶属关系的正常范围内"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lyipthaq68","created":1716968451973,"text":"如果计算的拷贝数是正态的，接受原假设；否则拒绝原假设"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1ly8t4k0h6o","created":1716967675531,"text":"根据鉴定出的ARG亚型/变异特征或每个品系的ARG族的权重系数，进一步定义和计算作为解释指标的评分指数"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d1lz9tnxvn5s","created":1716970576178,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d1lz76sr9fcw","created":1716970369675,"text":"分支主题","priority":3},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-green-compat","version":"1.4.43"}